Description_lang: Harnesses electrical currents around the caster to create a magnetic field that grows in power the longer it is channeled. Creatures caught in the area of effect are pulled toward the caster. Players within $120101A1 yards of the caster suffer $120101m1 Nature damage every $t2 seconds.
